JAPI  
JavaPartialFunction<A,B> Helper for implementing a *pure* partial function: it will possibly be invoked multiple times for a single “application”, because its only abstract method is used for both isDefinedAt() and apply(); the former is mapped to isCheck == true and the latter to isCheck == false for those cases where this is important to know.
